entry.title: About Me
entry.content:
Hi guys, this is Wu Beibei. I was born in 1999, rasied in a small town from SouthEastern China. Majored in mechanics, I’ve got my bachelor’s degree in Tongji University and my master’s degree in Shanghai Jiao Tong University. Check my github for more info.
